The usage of DRadiSurfTomo is quite similar to
DSurfTomo (Fang et al 2015)
and
DAzimSurfTomo (Liu et al 2019)

Here are some notes that may be useful.

1. model setup

This code takes two input model files;
- MOD.Vsv - initial Vsv model, in same format as DSurfTomo
- MOD.gam - initial gamma model, in same format as velocity model

And up to two input data files, each containing either Rayleigh or Love dispersion data.
These should be separate.

